  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add thinly sliced red onion and cook until caramelized, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add ground pork and cook, breaking it up with a spoon, until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add rendered pork fat, fish sauce, lime juice, soy sauce, and sugar. Stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, until the flavors have melded together.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in chopped cilantro and scallions.",
